Redis With Mongodb

Make use of redis and mongodb to create applications that perform better.
First save list of city in the mongodb
Url for data: https://developerfunnel.herokuapp.com/location

Now the user will send the city name in query params. 
First check data is part of redis if not that search in Mongo.

If Find in mongo moves to redis and returns the output.

Bonus: If you can connect with react and make UI.